feature: Hotel Booking In Adcation Booking

Scenario: Login Page

Given user launch The Application

When User Enter The UserName In UserName Field

And User Enter The Password In Password Field

Then User Click On The Login Button And It Navigates To Search Button

Scenario: Search Hotel Page

When User Select the Hotel Page

And User Select Room Type

And User Select Number Of Rooms 

And User Select Check in Date

And User Select Check Out Date

And User Select Adults Per Rooms

And User Select Childern Per Rooms

Then User Click On The Search Button And It Navigates To The Continue

Scenario:Continue Button

When User Select Hotel

Then User Click On The Search Button And It Navigates To The Continue

Scenario: Continue Button

When User Select Hotel

Then User Click On The Continue And It Navigates To The Book Now 

When User The First Name In First Name Field 

And User Enter The Last Name In Last Name Field

And User Enter The Address In Address Field

And User Enter The Credit Card Number In Credit Card Number In Field

And User Enter The Credit Card Type In Credit Card Type In Field

And User Enter The Expiry Date In Expiry Date In Field

And User Enter The CVV Number In CVV Number In Field   

Then User Click On The Book Now And It Navigates To The Book Confirmation